Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:07.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:11.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:16.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:52.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:02.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:12.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:17.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:28.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:41.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:46.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:56.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:07.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:12.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:18.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:24.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:39.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:46.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:52.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你干了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙又打算制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类只要乖乖变成石头就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要把人类当作这么低等的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类可以制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石可以制作人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么人造人可以制作出什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生出什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只带来破坏的东西能叫做神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为自己成为了完全的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是走到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就生出人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到长生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克塞鲁克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于得到身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猩律斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好 把我也搭上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要一个知道情况的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个叫父亲大人的人造人老大在乱闹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能战斗的人要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的青蛙和两个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不指挥谁指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是说指挥不指挥的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不受你的指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从本部来的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战本部 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们那边情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半被吹飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和北门无法取得联络
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那家伙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表是普通的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在体内有数十万人份的贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个能量把神之力吞入体内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师的话 应该知道这个厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人就在这里下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的部下还在上面战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他们的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本部说想和您通话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不用担心 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们布里克斯兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使老板不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能毫无畏惧地自主行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器库 黄队 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东门 蓝队 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听那边的对话您是受着伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在那里看着我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚力士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上通信机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 走了 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你们两个都是伤者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的贤者之石由我来烧尽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个目的需要中尉的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作是保护少主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死在这种地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打倒他的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到这里来的时候已经满身创伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是这样的话 我也就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕卡尼亚大尉和清国的人协力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予了布拉德雷致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的部下很强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅 你没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人 你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…护着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人 阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍…霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是2个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是金色长发的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别和钢之炼金术师弄混了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东门 蓝队 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西门 白队 白队跑到司令部西栋阴影下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 钢 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这点攻击没任何效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给他反击的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 一副满不在乎的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我接各队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止攻击 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向12点钟方向修正
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛看不见不知道要多少火力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有控制火力的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离50
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 53
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这双手合掌的炼成还真不太习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面 攻击来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真便利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击 攻击 不断攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别给他反击的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他不断地使用贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界能全部变成我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所说的得到世界是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果得到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就全是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身体里的空虚也许就能填上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能填补自出生以来一直持续的饥渴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太肤浅了 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的应该不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上嘴 小毛孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是强欲的古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的东西一定会弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒸笼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没效果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想办法搞定那个防御壁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹不够了 再多补充些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没意义的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类休想碰我一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得真是时候 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是孝顺的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是我需要贤者之石的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去掉防御壁就没法夺取贤者之石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 反过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没想过自己的神之力会被反噬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来收下全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手…防御了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再压制神了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头 石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅 我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥用自己的右臂换回了我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 相反也是可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要给我做条路就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了那种事情 阿尔冯斯大人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事只能拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要胜哦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 接下来就相信哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 灵魂进来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会来带你走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会 绝对会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人期待会牺牲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行 能行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拼命想要获得的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是像他们一样的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 三流的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你看看我们之间的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那力量是带来一切之物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.89,0:24:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是为了保护最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第63话 门的那边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见证一切
